    dc:description "Figures 102 - 109. Male of Zeugodacus umiam David & Kennedy, sp. nov. 102 head (frontal view) 103 scutum (dorsal view) 104 thorax (lateral view) and legs 105 abdomen 106 wing 107 epandrium and surstyli (lateral view) 108 epandrium and surstyli (posterior view) 109 glans of phallus." ;
